{"tid":2087211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊：睇吓有啲咩係可以真正為香港爭取到","createTime":"2020-06-30T15:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T07:18:38.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":504,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3bd03c7ca8f4c2ad54b07cb7d68b566b060a5c","tid":2087211,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"事到如今，我都係果句，既然冇得反對，不如睇吓有啲咩係可以真正為香港爭取到。<br />\n六月頭，我同幾位希望聯盟嘅發起人出咗封信比人大委員長栗戰書委員。既然人大決心要通過港版國安法，就算幾不盡香港人意，都不能齋噏當做咗野，點都要為香港在此框架下爭取到實際嘅嘢，例如不設有追溯期、用普通法條文、執行架構要由香港人組成及香港審訊等。<br />\n睇完今日嘅新聞，有太多感慨，有人走到，但係有好多香港人走唔到，走唔到就惟有在能力之內爭取，才是上策。詳細條文應該差不多出嚟，我只想大家平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/247953171912743/posts/4037289192979103/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F247953171912743%2Fposts%2F4037289192979103%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e0935fd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/247953171912743/posts/4037289192979103/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d583456d5dba563e442ad4725462a31c2eda7e3d","tid":2087211,"uid":10014,"like":112,"dislike":3,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"屌 鱷魚淚？"},{"pid":"ecdcd548fe9103208a1ef8352d7f84abf28aaea2","tid":2087211,"uid":337210,"like":254,"dislike":0,"score":254,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"仲爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人強姦緊爭取佢帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e826d4f192283e5f15baa8e77994c05775f855","tid":2087211,"uid":19527,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"小田：<br />\n<br />\n閱<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n栗戰書"},{"pid":"1a44541fa49fae28409916372bacf13a7b5b07f2","tid":2087211,"uid":87780,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"你同袁彌昌收皮啦"},{"pid":"bfd7cdb7dd70e7c6e73edfcacfa2c286a977e7aa","tid":2087211,"uid":173179,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事到如今，我都係果句，既然冇得反對，不如睇吓有啲咩係可以真正為香港爭取到。<br />\n六月頭，我同幾位希望聯盟嘅發起人出咗封信比人大委員長栗戰書委員。既然人大決心要通過港版國安法，就算幾不盡香港人意，都不能齋噏當做咗野，點都要為香港在此框架下爭取到實際嘅嘢，例如不設有追溯期、用普通法條文、執行架構要由香港人組成及香港審訊等。<br />\n睇完今日嘅新聞，<span style=\"color: red;\">有太多感慨，有人走到，但係有好多香港人走唔到</span>，走唔到就惟有在能力之內爭取，才是上策。詳細條文應該差不多出嚟，我只想大家平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/247953171912743/posts/4037289192979103/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F247953171912743%2Fposts%2F4037289192979103%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e0935fd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/247953171912743/posts/4037289192979103/?d=n</a></blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880be360c91b16c4a8d657b20c3b88ec8b868bb2","tid":2087211,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"多撚謝"},{"pid":"f998029b866d09095ed5cdd8bbd94da759e1acf7","tid":2087211,"uid":39846,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"你死撚左佢算啦&hellip;&hellip;「田少殉港」咁咪為香港爭取到國際注意囉&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ff5071f41e22852477cd2644af02a5c1f31d4688","tid":2087211,"uid":4783,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"份垃圾寫到咁辣<br />\n爭取咩野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e03fe385a85e8011fd3d90f310ad489cb08b1a2","tid":2087211,"uid":88743,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">終於要靠中間派幫香港人爭取了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i