pid":"24aeb1bf03ae7b6a24cfed7ebd836aabf425d8a0","tid":2087211,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"反對，阻礙政策 ，違反惡安法<br />\n田少rip"},{"pid":"44363232167ad6a40c52be24c29cc65d2f44a7a0","tid":2087211,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"夠膽投反對票<br />\n可以抄家"},{"pid":"5fec0637324bce9c0f7078925b91e82b15ddf54e","tid":2087211,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:21:07.000Z","msg":"殖民政府&lt;&lt;國安法&gt;&gt;簡單解釋<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2087350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2087350</a>"},{"pid":"2cecfc997511c98b37ca895156f64b79f98c663b","tid":2087211,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"0dc46ce13ee58d82b9eddf85d030597dc464dc6a","tid":2087211,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六月四日</span><br />\n咩意思？"},{"pid":"de3c64c3593bd99c93b76aa6d398d45488998ccf","tid":2087211,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"你當年阻住23條立法, 你顧掂自己先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b847d501af3aecea6a91aef1d14a22621bdb45a0","tid":2087211,"uid":17379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"田少咁講已經犯法"},{"pid":"15ce06b2bc69e7910c9d6a3326e702e498575d6d","tid":2087211,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"失敗左啦, 仲講"},{"pid":"61ab6bfd1617ac4eafcce87d4b1d4b2172ac0630","tid":2087211,"uid":102835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"你成日批評政府以為走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba0ff16b9af6ba5246f933e06a99087122113d5","tid":2087211,"uid":235608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"田生你唔同意由國家自己執行國安法？ 拉"},{"pid":"0056f650db28b1d5e1a20ba35b3e8372b22a59ee","tid":2087211,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"推 7.1大遊行 tweet國際戰線 黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"d838076eae25bb51c47892149bbe0fced68ef003","tid":2087211,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdcd548fe9103208a1ef8352d7f84abf28aaea2","tid":2087211,"uid":337210,"like":254,"dislike":0,"score":254,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"仲爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人強姦緊爭取佢帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"田少話係務實<i